### Obter Perfil do Usuário por ID (UUID)
GET http://localhost:8080/usuarios/6009694b-0958-4ffd-a480-928eef180184/perfil
Accept: application/json

### Obter status do usuário através do IDs (UUIDs separados por vírgula)
GET http://localhost:8080/usuarios/status?ids=17fda6b0-84b0-4553-85b8-5dca56a0e888,6009694b-0958-4ffd-a480-928eef180184
Accept: application/json

### Consultar Informações do Vendedor
@ID_DO_USUARIO = 6009694b-0958-4ffd-a480-928eef180184
GET http://localhost:8080/usuarios/{{ID_DO_USUARIO}}/seller-info
Accept: application/json

### Deletar (Inativar) Usuário
DELETE http://localhost:8080/usuarios/1f23b13f-c7b0-4a10-8366-55db05c134c2